Model Equations

Reactive Aggression Equations

Level 1: \[re_{ti}=\beta_{0i}+\beta_{1i}time_{ti}+\beta_{2i}nchildren_{ti}+\beta_{3i}group_{ti} + \beta_{4i}time_{ti} \times nchildren_{ti}\] \[+ \beta_{5i} nchildren_{ti} \times group_{ti} + \beta_{6i} time_{ti} \times group_{ti} + \beta_{7i}time_{ti} \times nchildren_{ti} \times group_{ti} + \beta_{8i}miss_{ti} +e_{ti}\]

Level 2: \[\beta_{0i}=\gamma_{00}+u_{0i}\] \[\beta_{1i}=\gamma_{10}+u_{1i}\]

\[\beta_{2i}=\gamma_{20}+u_{2i}\] \[\beta_{3i}=\gamma_{30}+u_{3i}\]

\[\beta_{4i}=\gamma_{40}+u_{4i}\]

\[\beta_{5i}=\gamma_{50}+u_{5i}\] \[\beta_{6i}=\gamma_{60}+u_{6i}\]

\[\beta_{7i}=\gamma_{70}+u_{7i}\] \[\beta_{8i}=\gamma_{80}+u_{8i}\] ### Proactive Aggression Equations

Level 1: \[pro_{ti}=\beta_{0i}+\beta_{1i}time_{ti}+\beta_{2i}nchildren_{ti}+\beta_{3i}group_{ti} + \beta_{4i}time_{ti} \times nchildren_{ti}\] \[+ \beta_{5i} nchildren_{ti} \times group_{ti} + \beta_{6i} time_{ti} \times group_{ti} + \beta_{7i}time_{ti} \times nchildren_{ti} \times group_{ti} + \beta_{8i}miss_{ti} +e_{ti}\]

Level 2: \[\beta_{0i}=\gamma_{00}+u_{0i}\] \[\beta_{1i}=\gamma_{10}+u_{1i}\]

\[\beta_{2i}=\gamma_{20}+u_{2i}\] \[\beta_{3i}=\gamma_{30}+u_{3i}\]

\[\beta_{4i}=\gamma_{40}+u_{4i}\]

\[\beta_{5i}=\gamma_{50}+u_{5i}\]

\[\beta_{6i}=\gamma_{60}+u_{6i}\]

\[\beta_{7i}=\gamma_{70}+u_{7i}\]

\[\beta_{8i}=\gamma_{80}+u_{8i}\] ## Spaghetti Plots - Test of Linearity

Attrition Analysis

cmdat <- cmdat %>%
  # Compute summaries by rows
  rowwise() %>%
  # First compute the number of missing occasions
  mutate(miss = sum(is.na(c_across(re:pro))),
         # Complete only when nmis_read = 0
         complete = if_else(miss == 0, "complete", "incomplete")) %>%
  ungroup()
# Compare the differences
datasummary((pro + re) ~
              complete * (Mean + SD), data = cmdat)
complete
incomplete
Mean SD Mean SD
pro 1.82 2.91 10.50 0.71
re 7.58 4.53 10.00 1.41
